# KPI Visibility Rules

- Render KPI settings and cards only when the current tab is Dashboard/Overview.
- Gate the entire KPI block with `currentTab === 'overview'`.
- Editing state (`kpiEditMode`) must be local to the overview section.

Reference implementation: [src/components/Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Dashboard.tsx)

Key snippet (do not duplicate outside Overview):

```tsx
{currentTab === 'overview' && (
  <DynamicKPISection /* ...props */ />
)}
```

